Name: Fantasy Mosaics 19: Edge of the World
About the game: Join the penguin family as they travel to the edge of the world to extend the mosaics color palette! This thrilling adventure brings a new challenging collection of puzzles and will lead you to explore a unique place along the way. Help the alien lady penguin as she is taking the penguin family on this expedition to make new discoveries. - Mosaic puzzles with an extended color palette - Pixel art puzzle challenges - Explore a new landscape - Puzzles based on logic
